  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We encourage youth to learn &amp; stand up for two important peace &amp; security issues: nuclear disarmament and climate activism. We will bring a group of youth to the 1st diplomatic meeting of the Nuclear Ban Treaty (March 2022 in Vienna, Austria); publish an inter-disciplinary journal examining connections between nuclear disarmament, environmental security, racial justice, and gender equity; and launch the &quot;Docuseries&quot;creative writing and art zine for First Nations young activists in Canada.</narrative>
  </description>
